g.title: j439408731
g.text: Can we talk about what you said earlier?

g.title: j411203391
g.text: I say a lot of things. Remind me?

g.title: j788222896
g.text: Forget what I said. Let's pretend it didn't happen. [End.]

g.title: j3548712521
g.text: You don't remember? How often do you go around confessing your feelings for people?

g.title: j2712245876
g.text: Did you mean what you said? Yes or no.

g.title: j3731900358
g.text: It's not that, I was just hoping *you'd* forget.

g.title: j1792064408
g.text: I'll cut you some slack because you've had a messed up life. I don't know why you said if you didn't mean it.

g.title: j2545812536
g.text: I need you to level with me, smartass.

g.title: j1294988390
g.text: I'm not sure what I expected...

g.title: j2003522008
g.text: But honestly? I don't care. Don't do it again.

g.title: j1129041723
g.text: I'm supposed to be "the boss" now, right? The one in charge.

g.title: j945825335
g.text: I mean. I showed you my hand. And you peaced out.

g.title: j1454109154
g.text: I told you how I felt, and you left me hanging.

g.title: j1392569353
g.text: Things have changed. A lot. In such a short span of time.

g.title: j2081004139
g.text: Doesn't mean you can't be vulnerable. Trust me.

g.title: j2706203397
g.text: I'd be a fool not to let myself change with it. To not be willing to at least try.

g.title: j3693217456
g.text: Don't make my mistakes. Don't let yourself get cold.

g.title: j1527070551
g.text: When you arrived, I saw someone *just* like me - someone who wasn't really living, just surviving.

g.title: j89335658
g.text: And...that's part of what you've shown me since you've arrived.

g.title: j2695388229
g.text: How cold I've grown. How closed off. Even to my friends.

g.title: j3054067786
g.text: And that gave me hope. Hope I haven't allowed myself to have in a long time.

g.title: j3290807082
g.text: So...I had to think. And I'm sorry if that rubbed you the wrong way. But I had to let myself come to terms with the fact that, well.

g.title: j3715210344
g.text: I feel the same way about you.

g.title: j1143703203
g.text: So. Shall we make this official? Make this a "thing?"

g.title: j3774430668
g.text: I'm sorry. I'm not ready for this. [Do not date Arthur.]

g.title: j2827681664
g.text: Every time I think you can't get any more deranged...

g.title: j4111275920
g.text: Well, then. Let's see where the future takes us, hm?

g.title: j2687543056
g.text: I can respect that. Let me know if you change your mind.

g.title: j738302445
g.text: I, for one, am looking forward to it for the first time in...ages.
